-- string-upper-crystal.cell: uppercase conversion crystallization
-- Tests: soft→hard crystallization, string ops

⊢ to-upper
  given text ≡ "hello world"
  yield result

  ∴ Convert «text» to uppercase.

  ⊨ result = "HELLO WORLD"

⊢ crystallize
  given §to-upper
  given to-upper→result
  yield §to-upper', is-faithful

  ∴ Read «§to-upper». It converts text to uppercase.
    Write a ⊢= expression using Cell primitives: upper(text)
    Return the crystallized cell definition and whether it's faithful.

⊢ verify-crystal
  given §to-upper'
  given crystallize→is-faithful
  yield approved

  ∴ Check: does «§to-upper'» produce "HELLO WORLD" for input "hello world"?

  ⊨ approved = true
